= Yoshi's Cookie (NES) - ROM Map =

This page documents the ROM structure for '''Yoshi's Cookie''' (NES).

== Overview ==

Yoshi's Cookie is a puzzle game developed by Bullet-Proof Software and published by Nintendo in 1992. It uses NROM mapper (iNES mapper 0) with 32 KB PRG-ROM and 8 KB CHR-ROM.

